      "category": "breaking",
      "takeaway": "Marigold60 Interest Check Story One of the great things about custom keyboards, aside from the sound and feel, is the visual appeal. There is something special in keyboard design, considering that such simple shapes possess so much character. I was long fascinated by this, in particular the engraved weights, which always left a strong impression on me. It truly is an elegance unique to this community. Around a year ago, I wished that keyboards would externalize this beauty, rather than hiding it underneath–that was how this project began. As a solo designer, it has been a long journey for me.",
